summary: Mixed enb is an enb that focus on outside ,mainly in the light
descriptionHtml:
[color=#ff0000][u][b]
[size=6] Introduction[/size]
[/b][/u][/color] This enb is as the name suggests it's a mix of 3 enbs(credits) and it focus on outside and in the light , so if i don't want to  headache[color=#0000ff] [/color][color=#ffff00][u]decrease the brightness [/u] [/color]in Options>display>brightness
[img]https://scontent-gru1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpt1/t31.0-8/12068917_765039843625055_1231888630451268792_o.jpg[/img][color=#ffff00][u]
[/u][/color]
[color=#ff0000][size=6] [b][u]Instalation
[/u][/b][/size][/color] First , download the [url=http://enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0102.html]ENB Series 102[/url] and copy the "d3d9" file in to your skyrim's folder  , after that extract the "Mixed ENB" to your game folder too and enjoy the enb =D
